reviewText: Okay - so it's a little dated.  But this is the Bond film that introduced, not the Bond girl, but the Bond Car!  And the Aston Martin entered immortality through this car!  It also had, of course, the Bond girl "Pussy Galore" who was already a known British actress from the British "Avengers" television series - Honour Blackman.  A fine film and an excellent Bond!  Just look past the date and enjoy!
